<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
I found a ring of slaying (+17, +17)    -- the hardcoded maximum <p>
I tried to make it indestructible so I can artifact it. Then it was (+9, +1). Then removing indestructible didn't change it. 
</p>
<p>
This is a soul-crushing bug for alchemists! 
</p>
<p>
Can we prevent all rerolling when making indestructible, same as when removing indestructible?? This may help save other great rings. Thanks. 
</p>
